        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2091290758" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9480824809614523338">What a hilariously sarcastic play! I thoroughly enjoyed the antics of Don Juan and his morally tested valet, Sganarelle. <br/> The play was pulled after only 15 viewings because the censors found it a mockery of the church. <br/> Excellent!! 😁👏🏻🎭</span>

