<div id="review_3354355214" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3354355214" />
    <a title="Marian" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/8034691-marian"><img alt="Marian" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1611283992p2/8034691.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3354355214?book_show_action=true">May 24, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Marian" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Marian" href="/user/show/8034691-marian">Marian</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3354355214" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer906257789759622890">I think this would have been more enjoyable if the character of Don Juan had not already permeated cultural references, which is how I came to know the story more or less before I&apos;d read it. For me the reading was highly predictable and not as fun as some of Moliere&apos;s other plays.</span>
  <span id="freeText906257789759622890" style="display:none">I think this would have been more enjoyable if the character of Don Juan had not already permeated cultural references, which is how I came to know the story more or less before I'd read it. For me the reading was highly predictable and not as fun as some of Moliere's other plays.</span>
  <a data-text-id="906257789759622890" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
